<sect>Avance Logic
<p>
<descrip>
<tag>&legacyvers;:</tag>
	Support for the AL2101, ALI2228, ALI2301, ALI2302, ALI2308,
	ALI2401 chipsets.  The status of this support is unknown because
	we don't have any recent test reports.

<tag>&relvers;:</tag>
	No native support for any chipsets.  NEED TO CHECK IF
	fbdev OR SIMILAR WILL WORK FOR THEM.

</descrip>

